STEP|82|Docs: https://github.com/EleutherAI/lm-evaluation-harness/tree/main/docs
STEP|83|Task library: 60+ tasks including MMLU, GSM8K, HumanEval, TruthfulQA, HellaSwag, ARC, WinoGrande, etc.
STEP|84|Leaderboard: https://huggingface.co/spaces/HuggingFaceH4/open_llm_leaderboard (uses this harness)
